article_title: Is Alaska Gov. Bill Walker's Medicaid Expansion An Illegal Power Grab?

article_metadata.author: The Apothecary

og.description: In July, Alaska Governor Bill Walker (I) announced his intention to unilaterally implement Obamacare’s Medicaid expansion. But Gov. Walker’s unilateral Obamacare expansion isn’t just bad policy, it’s also likely illegal.
